<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!--
==============================================================================
VSTGUI UIDescription - Iterum Delay Plugin
==============================================================================
11 delay modes with 113+ automatable parameters.
Uses CViewSwitchContainer to show only the selected mode's panel.

GUI Layout Redesign (Spec 040): Controls organized into labeled groups
by functionality. Group order: Primary controls first, specialized later.
==============================================================================
-->
